### ─── AUTH ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login — admin Clínica San Marcos
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@sanmarcos.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login — super admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "super@atiende.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login — doctor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "dr.garcia@sanmarcos.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login — admin Clínica Vita (tenant diferente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@vita.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Me — quién soy
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout

### ─── TENANTS ──────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar tenants (solo super_admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Crear clínica (super_admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Clínica Nueva",
  "slug": "clinica-nueva",
  "city": "Lima"
}

### Mi clínica (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tenants/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Editar mi clínica (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tenants/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone": "044-999999",
  "city": "Trujillo"
}

### ─── USERS ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar usuarios del tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── HEALTH ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health